    statement: { description: "## Construct Smallest Window with All Distinct Characters\n\nGiven a string `s`, find the smallest window (substring) that contains all the distinct characters of the string.\n\nFor example, if `s = 'aabcbcdbca'`, there are 4 distinct characters (a, b, c, d), and the smallest window containing all of them is `'dbca'`.", inputFormat: "A single line containing the string `s`.", outputFormat: "Print the length of the smallest window containing all distinct characters.", constraints: "1 ≤ |s| ≤ 10^5\nOnly lowercase English letters.", notes: "" },
